snippet.title: Navicula Meatus game trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3203590/Navicula_Meatus/
Demo will be coming soon.

Game trailer for the upcoming game Navicular Meatus created by Torgomind. For updates and more info check:
https://www.torgomind.com/
https://store.steampowered.com/developer/torgomind/

"A dark and surreal puzzle adventure set in a decaying town where veins pulse through ruined structures and the night hums with unfamiliar life."
